data.description: JUST REDUCED! STUNNING, ENERGY EFFICIENT, CUL DE SAC LA COSTA HOME WITH A LARGE FLAT LOT AND VIEWS IN THE SOUGHT-AFTER CARLSBAD SCHOOL DISTRICT! VAULTED CEILINGS, A TRULY OPEN FLOORPLAN, AND A SENSE OF MODERN ELEGANCE GREET YOU AS YOU ENTER THE HOME. THE NEWLY REMODELED CHEF'S KITCHEN IS THE HEART OF THE HOME AND IS BEAUTIFULLY APPOINTED WITH A FARMHOUSE SINK, HANDMADE TILE BACKSPLASH, CONVENTION OVEN/MULTI BURNER STOVE AND HOOD, SOFT CLOSE DRAWERS, GORGEOUS COUNTERTOPS WITH SEATING AND A VIEW! THE BACK YARD! SIT UNDER THE ARBOUR ENJOYING THE VIEW, PLAY GAMES IN THE GRASS OR JUST ENJOY THE PRIVACY AND QUIET. THE GRAND STAIRCASE IS PERFECTLY PLACED AND GIVES THE HOME A LARGER FEEL. THE MASTER SUITE IS A DREAM WITH A BATHROOM YOU WILL WANT TO LIVE IN. THE NEW OWNED SOLAR, NEW ELECTRIC OR GAS HAVC, NEW DUCTING AND A CAR CHARGING STATION MAKE THIS AN ENERGY-EFFICIENT HOME THAT IS EASY TO HEAT AND COOL AND WILL SAVE BIG ON YOUR SDGE BILL. GORGEOUS FIXTURES, LIGHTING, AND FINISHES THROUGHOUT THE HOME AND A WATER SOFTENER. NEWER ROOF RELAY. VIEWS FROM MOST OF THE ROOMS IN THE HOME. A SPACIOUS 3-CAR GARAGE WITH AN EXTRA LARGE DRIVEWAY ALONG WITH THE MOST ATTRACTIVE ELEVATION IN THIS TRACT MAKES IT A MUST-SEE. AVIARA OAKS MS, POINSETTIA ES.
